OL,5,G1858 This is BBC Four
OL,6,G1900 University Challenge
OL,7,     F27/37. Two more teams begin their
OL,8,     Fquarter-final campaigns, hoping to
OL,9,     Fsecure the first of the two wins
OL,10,     Fthey need to progress to the
OL,11,     Fsemi-finals. Jeremy Paxman asks
OL,12,     Fthe questions.
