OL,5,G2150 One Foot in Arthur's Seat
OL,6,     FActor Ian Richardson walks up the
OL,7,     Fhill to Arthur's Seat, which
OL,8,     Foverlooks the city of Edinburgh,
OL,9,     Fas he did during lunch hours as a
OL,10,     Fbored office clerk 50 years ago.
OL,11,G2200 W Stephen Gilbert Remembers...
OL,12,G     Only Connect
OL,13,     FProducer W Stephen Gilbert looks
OL,14,     Fback on the 1979 TV play Only
OL,15,     FConnect.
OL,16,G2215 The Other Side: Only Connect
OL,17,     FYoung academic Graham visits the
OL,18,     Felderly John to learn more about
OL,19,     Fpioneering socialist and gay
OL,20,     Frights campaigner Edward Carpenter
OL,21,     Ffor his thesis on the early UK
OL,22,     FLabour movement.
